{"text_id":230328,"tokens":["The"," method"," by"," which"," the"," president"," of"," the"," United"," States"," is"," elected"," is"," a"," perennial"," issue"," that"," is"," frequently"," debated","."," While"," there"," are"," positives"," to"," both"," the"," Electoral"," College"," and"," popular"," vote"," systems",","," I"," believe"," that"," the"," Electoral"," College"," is"," the"," best"," option"," for"," electing"," the"," president",".","\n\n","One"," significant"," advantage"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," is"," its"," ability"," to"," ensure"," that"," smaller"," states"," have"," a"," voice"," in"," the"," election"," process","."," Under"," a"," popular"," vote"," system",","," states"," with"," larger"," populations"," would"," inevitably"," have"," a"," greater"," influence"," on"," the"," outcome",","," potentially"," neglecting"," the"," interests"," of"," smaller"," states","."," The"," Electoral"," College",","," however",","," alloc","ates"," votes"," based"," on"," the"," number"," of"," electors",","," rather"," than"," the"," population"," of"," each"," state","."," This"," means"," that"," every"," state"," has"," a"," minimum"," of"," three"," electors",","," guaranteeing"," that"," smaller"," states"," cannot"," be"," overlooked",".","\n\n","Another"," benefit"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," is"," its"," ability"," to"," act"," as"," a"," firewall"," against"," extreme"," candidates","."," Candidates"," who"," may"," have"," limited"," appeal"," on"," a"," national"," level"," could"," theoretically"," win"," a"," popular"," vote"," by"," narrowly"," dominating"," a"," few"," large"," states","."," However",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," necessitates"," candidates"," to"," build"," a"," broader"," coalition",","," as"," they"," need"," to"," win"," votes"," in"," a"," diverse"," array"," of"," states","."," This"," helps"," to"," ensure"," that"," the"," winner"," of"," an"," election"," is"," a"," candidate"," with"," broader"," appeal"," and"," is"," capable"," of"," representing"," the"," interests"," of"," a"," wider"," cross","-","section"," of"," Americans","."," ","\n\n","While"," there"," are"," certainly"," drawbacks"," to"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system",","," such"," as"," the"," possibility"," of"," '","faith","less","'"," electors"," disrupting"," the"," election"," result"," or"," disputes"," arising"," from"," the"," popular"," vote",","," I"," believe"," that"," the"," positives"," of"," this"," system"," outweigh"," these"," potential"," issues","."," Ultimately",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," serves"," as"," a"," more"," democratic"," system"," that"," provides"," every"," state"," with"," a"," voice"," and"," helps"," to"," prevent"," extreme"," candidates"," from"," taking"," office","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," go"," into"," more"," detail"," about"," any"," of"," the"," points"," I","'","ve"," made","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}